{"type":"message","id":"149e1293","parentId":"9afc4c08","timestamp":"2026-03-17T20:01:17.122Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Yn8C4a3Fp4AdACcxzDDMI9xz","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773777677121}}
{"type":"message","id":"f32d2d58","parentId":"149e1293","timestamp":"2026-03-17T20:01:17.124Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_YSZrzeIcTy28TXb5WXXhmVd9","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Checklist: Heartbeat Workspace Backup\n\n## Trigger\n- 每天检查一次 `~/.openclaw` 是否有未提交修改\n\n## Pre-flight\n- [ ] 进入 `~/.openclaw`\n- [ ] 运行 `git status`\n- [ ] 确认不包含敏感信息（credentials / tokens / secrets）\n\n## Execution\n- [ ] 按修改类型分组提交：\n  - skill / config / workspace / docs / chore\n- [ ] 执行 `git add -A`\n- [ ] 执行 `git commit -m \"[类型] 更新描述\"`\n- [ ] 执行 `git push`\n\n## Verification\n- [ ] 推送成功\n- [ ] 如有需要，记录到 `memory/heartbeat-backup-log.md`\n\n## Notes\n- 敏感信息不要提交\n- 优先保证重要工作区修改已同步\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773777677123}}
{"type":"message","id":"9bcf83db","parentId":"f32d2d58","timestamp":"2026-03-17T20:01:17.125Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_xFhSElAEzzyBk25FLJDNfNry","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Checklist: Heartbeat Quant Ops\n\n## 08:50 Morning News Push Check\n\n### State File\n```bash\ncat ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json\n```\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 检查 `status` / `generated_at` / `last_success_at` / `last_failure_at`\n- [ ] 若交易日 08:50 之后仍无当日成功记录，主动汇报阻断原因\n- [ ] 若 `status` 为 `GENERATION_FAILED` 或 `PUSH_FAILED`，主动汇报错误摘要与日志路径\n- [ ] 若已成功且无新增变化，保持安静\n\n## Quant Research Mainline Health\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 scripts/run_investment_research_mainline_guard.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_YYYYMMDD.json`\n- 终端摘要：`🩺 量化投研主链巡检：OK/WARN/ALERT`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 检查退出码与 `overall_status`\n- [ ] `ALERT`：主动汇报晨报 / 稳定策略 / 回测队列是哪一项断裂\n- [ ] `WARN`：汇报缺口文件或未生成入口\n- [ ] `OK` 且无新增变化：保持安静\n\n## Trading-day Premarket Precheck (09:20-09:40)\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/auto_run_premarket_precheck.py --available-cash 1000000 --account-nav 930000\n```\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 无需用户提醒，交易日自动执行\n- [ ] 当日已执行过则跳过\n- [ ] 非交易日保持安静\n- [ ] 失败时主动汇报阻断原因与报告路径\n- [ ] 成功时汇报 `precheck` / `orders` / `brief` 路径\n\n## Daily Strategy Audit\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/run_daily_strategy_audit.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_YYYYMMDD.json`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] `PASS`：简要汇报核心指标与路径\n- [ ] `ALERT`：主动汇报未通过项与修复建议\n\n## Daily Enhancements\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/run_daily_enhancements.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/sector_heatmap_latest.html`\n- `research/reports/sector_heatmap_summary.json`\n- `research/reports/daily_enhancement_YYYYMMDD.json`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 双源验证失败：主动告警\n- [ ] 热力图失败：主动告警\n- [ ] 正常运行：简要汇报上涨/下跌板块数\n\n## Live Dashboard + Feishu Push\n\n### Commands\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/sync_ths_app_data.py\npython3 scripts/sync_ths_exports.py\npython3 scripts/generate_live_global_dashboard.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/live_global_dashboard_latest.html`\n- `research/reports/live_global_dashboard_YYYYMMDD.html`\n\n### Push Rules\n- [ ] 成功后主动发飞书 DM：面板路径、precheck 状态、年化/回撤/夏普、买卖记录数、A股温度摘要\n- [ ] `needs_permission=true`：提示给 OpenClaw/终端 Full Disk Access\n- [ ] 导出为空：提示“同花顺暂无可用导出数据/账户为空”\n- [ ] 生成失败：主动发报错摘要与修复建议\n- [ ] 非交易时段不含“可执行买价”，只给预算/优先级/开盘触发条件\n- [ ] 当天已推送且无新增数据，可保持安静\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773777677124}}
{"type":"message","id":"453fc09e","parentId":"9bcf83db","timestamp":"2026-03-17T20:01:17.126Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_bkc8QtCOzCwHKGTFFLC19Q1X","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Checklist: Heartbeat Self-Improvement\n\n## Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/generate_daily_report.py\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/auto_promote_learnings.py --apply --threshold 2\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/auto_extract_skill_drafts.py --threshold 2\n```\n\n## Output\n- `memory/self_improvement_daily_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `memory/self_improvement_autopromote_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `memory/self_improvement_skill_drafts_YYYYMMDD.md`\n\n## Rules\n- [ ] 汇总 `.learnings/LEARNINGS.md` / `ERRORS.md` / `FEATURE_REQUESTS.md`\n- [ ] 统计高优先级待处理项、状态分布、area 分布\n- [ ] 对 `Recurrence-Count >= 2` 的 learning 自动提升到 `AGENTS.md / TOOLS.md / SOUL.md`\n- [ ] 对 `Recurrence-Count >= 2` 的 learning 生成 skill 草稿到 `skills/<name>/SKILL.md`\n- [ ] **只生成草稿，不自动安装**到 `~/.openclaw/skills/`\n- [ ] 无论有无提升项，都主动发飞书 DM 汇报摘要与三个输出文件路径\n- [ ] 若无提升项，明确写“今日无自动提升项”\n- [ ] 若无技能草稿，明确写“今日无技能草稿生成”\n- [ ] 若发生自动提升，汇报被提升条目、目标文件路径、写入是否成功\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773777677125}}
{"type":"message","id":"59348553","parentId":"453fc09e","timestamp":"2026-03-17T20:01:49.002Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering daily strategy**\n\nI’m thinking about whether to conduct a daily strategy audit or enhancement, especially since the Heartbeat checklists emphasize a daily internal execution. It’s 4 AM, so given that the user mentioned a heartbeat poll, maybe it makes sense to run the commands and check for any changes. If outputs have altered, it might be wise to report that a new file or report has landed. However, I need to balance that against the quiet hours for non-emergencies.**Evaluating tasks and updates**\n\nI’m considering how the heartbeat instructions work, which allow for proactive sends. But I wonder if the internal heartbeat trigger sends updates to the heartbeat channel instead of the user directly? I should check if any tasks have already run today; if they have and there are no new changes, it's all good. If not, maybe we should execute the necessary tasks. Since it’s 4 AM and related to backups, I might skip the morning news and focus on status updates instead.**Checking workspace health**\n\nI'm focusing on performing a final check using exec commands before moving forward. I need to check the status of my workspace backup with `git status`, and also verify the existence of several reports, like the morning state file, mainline health report, strategy audit report, daily enhancement report, live dashboard, and self-improvement reports.\n\nSince it's currently 4 AM, these checks might not have run yet, so maybe I'll run the commands only if something is missing. Let's inspect!","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_UWaAuvcUWC7CJkIUXq866EHb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -euo pipefail\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\nprintf '=== git status ===\\n'\ngit -C /Users/ling/.openclaw status --short || true\nprintf '\\n=== heartbeat artifacts today ===\\n'\nfor f in \\\n  memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json \\\n  research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_20260318.md \\\n  research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_20260318.json \\\n  quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_20260318.md \\\n  quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_20260318.json \\\n  quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/daily_enhancement_20260318.json \\\n  quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/live_global_dashboard_20260318.html \\\n  memory/self_improvement_daily_20260318.md \\\n  memory/self_improvement_autopromote_20260318.md \\\n  memory/self_improvement_skill_drafts_20260318.md\n do\n  if [ -e \"$f\" ]; then\n    stat -f '%Sm %N' -t '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S' \"$f\"\n  else\n    echo \"MISSING $f\"\n  fi\ndone\nprintf '\\n=== morning state summary ===\\n'\npython3 - <<'PY'\nimport json, os\np='/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json'\nif os.path.exists(p):\n    try:\n        d=json.load(open(p))\n        for k in ['status','generated_at','last_success_at','last_failure_at','error','log_path']:\n            if k in d:\n                print(f'{k}: {d[k]}')\n    except Exception as e:\n        print('state_parse_error:', e)\nelse:\n    print('state file missing')\nPY\n","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":30,"workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773777677126}}
