{"type":"message","id":"97b9f738","parentId":"5eee12fd","timestamp":"2026-03-18T00:01:18.174Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f7qGw5lpAssU3isRNdsFNb0l","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773792078172}}
{"type":"message","id":"b44ee2fd","parentId":"97b9f738","timestamp":"2026-03-18T00:01:31.746Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3kET6G6ldkpIfioBjwhfG1OC","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -euo pipefail\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 - <<'PY'\nimport json, os\nfrom pathlib import Path\npaths = {\n  'morning_state': Path('memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json'),\n  'health_json': Path('research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_20260318.json'),\n  'audit_json': Path('quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_20260318.json'),\n  'enh_json': Path('quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/daily_enhancement_20260318.json'),\n  'dashboard_html': Path('quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/live_global_dashboard_20260318.html'),\n  'self_daily': Path('memory/self_improvement_daily_20260318.md'),\n  'self_promote': Path('memory/self_improvement_autopromote_20260318.md'),\n  'self_drafts': Path('memory/self_improvement_skill_drafts_20260318.md'),\n}\nfor name,p in paths.items():\n    print(f'[{name}] exists={p.exists()} path={p}')\n    if p.exists():\n        print(f'  mtime={p.stat().st_mtime}')\n        if p.suffix == '.json':\n            try:\n                data=json.load(open(p))\n                if name=='morning_state':\n                    for k in ['status','generated_at','last_success_at','last_failure_at','error','log_path']:\n                        if k in data: print(f'  {k}={data[k]}')\n                if name=='health_json':\n                    print(f\"  overall_status={data.get('overall_status')}\")\n                    print(f\"  morning_news_status={data.get('snapshot',{}).get('morning_news_status')}\")\n                if name=='audit_json':\n                    print(f\"  overall_status={data.get('overall_status')}\")\n                if name=='enh_json':\n                    print(f\"  keys={list(data)[:10]}\")\n            except Exception as e:\n                print(f'  json_error={e}')\nPY","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":30,"workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773792078174}}
