{"type":"message","id":"c379f1b6","parentId":"05269ec6","timestamp":"2026-03-18T00:32:49.997Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Verifying file updates**\n\nI need to check if there are new results since 8:01. I could look at file modification times, but if there have been no changes since before 08:50, then nothing new has come up. It’s worth checking the daily enhancement file and seeing if the dashboard is still missing. I should verify that instead of assuming. Let’s read HEARTBEAT and possibly run a script to check relevant files and their states.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1zLaiawcRGNUy0FWtmF7NZYe","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773793956373}}
{"type":"message","id":"0af95d84","parentId":"c379f1b6","timestamp":"2026-03-18T00:32:50.031Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1zLaiawcRGNUy0FWtmF7NZYe","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773793970030}}
{"type":"message","id":"28326c80","parentId":"0af95d84","timestamp":"2026-03-18T00:33:06.117Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Checking for changes**\n\nI need to confirm that there are no new changes. I should check the modification time of the daily enhancement. There's a possibility that the dashboard updates are still missing, and perhaps no new dashboard was generated. It's also worth considering that the health status may remain the same. So, I'll do a quick execute to gather that information. Let's make sure everything is up-to-date!","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_KmrYVUyl5VSpWTHMwyHJTr43","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -euo pipefail\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 - <<'PY'\nimport os, json\nfrom pathlib import Path\nchecks = [\n    Path('memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json'),\n    Path('quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/daily_enhancement_20260318.json'),\n    Path('quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/sector_heatmap_summary.json'),\n    Path('quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/live_global_dashboard_20260318.html'),\n    Path('quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/ths_app_sync_summary_20260318.json'),\n    Path('quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/ths_sync_summary_20260318.json'),\n    Path('memory/self_improvement_daily_20260318.md'),\n    Path('memory/self_improvement_autopromote_20260318.md'),\n    Path('memory/self_improvement_skill_drafts_20260318.md'),\n]\nfor p in checks:\n    print(f'{p}|exists={p.exists()}')\n    if p.exists():\n        print(f'mtime={p.stat().st_mtime}')\n        if p.name == 'global_market_morning_0850_state.json':\n            d=json.load(open(p))\n            print('status=' + str(d.get('status')))\n            print('generated_at=' + str(d.get('generated_at')))\n          