{"type":"message","id":"6ff6768b","parentId":"2962d7be","timestamp":"2026-03-18T01:25:59.215Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_yYbfOiZ9jlta4nt3E9ZUkZic","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773797159214}}
{"type":"message","id":"3693917d","parentId":"6ff6768b","timestamp":"2026-03-18T01:26:23.118Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Inspecting heartbeat requirements**\n\nI need to follow the heartbeat closely and check the current status, possibly running a precheck for the scheduled work from 09:20 to 09:40. It likely helps to read the checklist, even though we went over it before. I should inspect existing outputs and maybe run commands related to these instructions to ensure compliance. Since it's a Wednesday and not a holiday in March 2026, I also need to check if anything has already been executed today.**Checking dashboard status and alerts**\n\nAt 9:25, I should alert if there's still no success or failure since the last check. The live dashboard is still down, so I need to see if anything has changed. I might need to run a precheck now if it hasn't been done yet. Since the heartbeat instructions mention only three proactive categories, I should also check the morning state file from yesterday. If the precheck runs successfully, it might help produce the necessary outputs or detect if the dashboard script now exists.**Reviewing workspace instructions**\n\nI need to consider the workspace instructions for procedure tasks, where I should continue without asking repeatedly. I could run a precheck and see if the daily heartbeat can check the workspace backup, though I'm uncertain about new situations since there are active issues. It’s important to execute scheduled work during the trading window and check if the precheck has been executed by cron. I also might need to inspect relevant files or check for an alternative path for dashboard generation. Reading the checklist again could help, but it might not be strictly necessary.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在处在 09:20-09:40 盘前强检窗口，我先核对今日产物并补跑强检。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_zArO062DDPlX1RYlIqZ19lvQ","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -euo pipefail\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 - <<'PY'\nimport json, os, glob\nfrom pathlib import Path\nbase = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports')\n# find today's precheck-like files\npatterns = [\n    'precheck*20260318*',\n    '*premarket*20260318*',\n    '*order*plan*20260318*',\n    '*orders*20260318*',\n    '*brief*20260318*'\n]\nseen=[]\nfor pat in patterns:\n    for p in sorted(base.glob(pat)):\n        seen.append(str(p))\nprint('\\n'.join(seen) if seen else 'NO_PRECHECK_ARTIFACTS')\nPY","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":30,"workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4Yfo0CsUQm1Q79PavCdqwqQJ","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -euo pipefail\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 - <<'PY'\nimport json, os\np='/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json'\nif os.path.exists(p):\n    d=json.load(open(p))\n    for k in ['status','generated_at','last_success_at','last_failure_at','error','log_path']:\n        print(f'{k}={d.get(k)}')\nelse:\n    print('MISSING')\nPY","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":30,"workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773797159216}}
