{"type":"message","id":"350228c0","parentId":"f18a71af","timestamp":"2026-03-18T06:56:29.135Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Checking dashboard status**\n\nI need to see if the dashboard is still missing since it was reported earlier. If there are no changes, I should respond with HEARTBEAT_OK. It's important to avoid inferring old tasks from previous chats and just assess the current situation. If everything still looks abnormal after the last check, I might keep quiet. I should verify if there are new reports or failures and inspect the modified times of key files. Let's read the heartbeat to be cautious and then check the modified times.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_h5J6Z9XOVVkKZpeWTkHyMTSb","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773816973876}}
{"type":"message","id":"d600d2b8","parentId":"350228c0","timestamp":"2026-03-18T06:56:29.191Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_h5J6Z9XOVVkKZpeWTkHyMTSb","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773816989190}}
